{"type":"message","id":"0ac63a58","parentId":"4431f13a","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:51:24.272Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_lMgQk2jm74R7kHWh9behfJ1A","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Self-Improvement Daily Report - 2026-03-16\n\n- 生成时间: 2026-03-16 13:51:07\n- 学习条目: 28\n- 错误条目: 4\n- 需求条目: 1\n- 待关注高优先级: 15\n- 可自动提升条目: 0\n\n## 状态分布\n- pending: 29\n- promoted: 2\n- resolved: 2\n\n## 优先级分布\n- critical: 1\n- high: 16\n- low: 4\n- medium: 12\n\n## Area 分布\n- backend: 5\n- config: 8\n- docs: 15\n- infra: 3\n- tests: 2\n\n## 高优先级待处理\n- LRN-20260308-002 | high | pending | 用户指出“多账户持仓抓取不准”，核心问题是把“账本缓存可读”误当作“账户切换已生效”，导致连续三轮结果一致却未在第一时间明确说明采集口径受限。\n- LRN-20260315-006 | high | pending | For future XTP integration, isolate all XTP SDK calls in a subprocess; never call InsertOrder directly from the main Python process due to callback deadlock risk\n- LRN-20260315-007 | high | pending | Do not mix XTP trading market enums with quote exchange enums; they are reversed between Shanghai and Shenzhen\n- LRN-20260315-008 | high | pending | Outside trading hours, XTP paper trading may reject limit orders because quotes are unavailable; scheduling must gate order placement to market hours\n- LRN-20260315-009 | high | pending | AKShare full-market A-share endpoint stock_zh_a_spot_em may fail outside mainland China; use single-stock queries or alternate data source fallback\n- LRN-20260315-010 | high | pending | Do not let AI generate stock picks or reports without an explicit data-backed decision path; ban vague 'common sense' justification\n- LRN-20260315-011 | high | pending | Preferred quant research system architecture: OpenClaw orchestration + multi-search MCP layer + layered market data + XTP subprocess isolation + cron-based monitoring windows\n- LRN-20260315-012 | high | pending | Do not restate external quant architecture as-is; adapt the system description to Zhang Ling's actual data stack, which includes Tushare and Yahoo Finance\n- LRN-20260315-013 | high | pending | When corrected on prior statements, revisit the workspace evidence before summarizing architecture; do not overwrite yesterday's documented data-source policy with a generic external template\n- LRN-20260315-014 | high | pending | When asked to learn from external examples, extract strengths and adapt them to the existing system instead of copying the architecture wholesale\n- LRN-20260315-015 | high | pending | Do not ask Zhang Ling whether to continue for procedural optimization work; continue automatically and interrupt only for important decisions\n- LRN-20260316-001 | high | pending | Asynchronous promises to continue work later must be converted into a verifiable execution chain in the same turn\n- LRN-20260316-002 | high | pending | Do not claim 'I’ll continue pushing app optimization myself' without verifiable follow-through in the stated time window\n- LRN-20260316-004 | high | pending | Do not promise '中午前修复' without device-level validation; report missed deadline directly\n- ERR-20260308-001 | critical | pending | 向用户直接回传了内部错误字符串：`403 OpenAI codex passthrough requires a non-empty instructions field`，影响沟通体验。 ClawHub registry unreachable when attempting to inspect/install camoufox-cli Heartbeat dashboard generation failed because scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py is missing in personal-a-share-research-system memory_store failed because LanceDB native module is missing on this host Daily investment research org runner failed once due to unterminated string literal in orchestrator markdown renderer Manual morning-news test could not use web_search because Brave API key is missing Role briefing generator failed once due to unterminated string literal in markdown section headers web_search unavailable because Brave API key is not configured on this host Shell probe for Android emulator tooling failed due to unmatched quote in printf block run_investment_research_review_ledger.py used JSON null literal in Python dict and crashed on first run Review ledger script selected the wrong org report because it sorted wildcard matches lexicographically instead of by freshness Overnight automation had a visible idle gap from 00:20 to 07:00 and the 08:50 morning report landed late at 08:54-08:55 Night autopilot instruction was treated as a plan document instead of a real scheduled execution chain, causing a 00:20-07:00 idle gap and missed 07:30 report Browser snapshot timed out after opening search result tabs, blocking browser-based web research fallback Progress on research-organization build was too slow because work stayed reactive and patch-driven instead of queue-driven and acceptance-oriented\n\n## 可自动提升候选\n- 无\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773640284269}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef8b8b88","parentId":"0ac63a58","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:51:56.404Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating heartbeat logic**\n\nI need to address the heartbeat logic and decide if anything needs attention. It's currently 13:50, and we only report if there's something specific like new files or script results, or if input or authorization is needed. However, the daily strategy audit ALERT and self-improvement require proactive communication. I can't inflect old tasks, so indicating \"nothing needs attention\" isn't accurate since there are outputs to report. It’s important to include crucial evidence and paths while remaining concise.**Considering self-improvement report**\n\nThe self-improvement checklist indicates I should proactively report outputs and paths, regardless of whether there are improvements. In this heartbeat session, I might need to mention the workspace backup, even though I need to avoid a markdown table. I checked the git status and found many uncommitted changes. Since the backup requires a push and could involve sensitive files, I should mention that \"workspace backup未执行，git status显示大量变更，需人工确认后再推\" to ensure any necessary user authorization. I think it's best to include this as it's relevant.**Checking heartbeat status**\n\nThe user specifically asked for a heartbeat check, so I need to respond concisely and only if something requires attention. It's crucial to mention that the backup needs manual confirmation due to the risk of sensitive information. While it might seem noisy, it’s genuinely a necessary user input as per the checklist. I should also note that the premarket precheck has already been run, and everything else, like the mainline health and morning news, is fine. The daily strategy audit alert indicates that some auto rules are disabled and the dashboard isn’t fresh.**Clarifying trading reports**\n\nIt looks like I’m trying to understand the current trading time in Shanghai, which is from 1:50 PM until 3:00 PM. However, I shouldn’t focus on executable buy prices. Instead, I can report heartbeat ops in the file. I’ll also consider mentioning local paths since they’re relevant, but if those can’t open in certain applications, it’s best to provide the key content instead of just the paths. It seems I’ll include both as evidence without solely relying on paths.**Summarizing self-improvement report**\n\nI need to create a self-improvement output summary in Chinese, specifically mentioning \"今日无自动提升项/无技能草稿生成.\" The report should default to Chinese for status words while keeping file paths in English. I might include details like the results of the strategy audit, which flagged something due to inactive pre-market rules. Additionally, I'll mention the workspace backup situation and sensitive directories needing user confirmation, but I’ll keep evidence concise. Including only key points from `git status` could be best instead of a full list.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 有 3 件事需要注意：\n\n- 每日策略审计已跑出结果，当前为告警。  \n  关键信息：策略健康本身通过，年化 55.07%、最大回撤 24.89%、夏普 2.794；但运行链路有两个缺口：  \n  1) 盘前自动执行规则未启用  \n  2) 模拟盘对比面板 24 小时内未更新  \n  证据文件：  \n  - `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_20260316.md`  \n  - `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_20260316.json`\n\n- self-improvement 日报已生成。  \n  今日摘要：学习条目 28、错误条目 4、高优先级待处理 15；今日无自动提升项，今日无技能草稿生成。  \n  证据文件：  \n  - `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/memory/self_improvement_daily_20260316.md`  \n  - `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/memory/self_improvement_autopromote_20260316.md`  \n  - `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_20260316.md`\n\n- workspace backup 这轮只完成了检查，未执行提交/推送。  \n  原因：`git status` 显示大量变更，且夹杂会话、媒体、配置等高风险路径，不适合在未筛选前直接外推；这一步如果继续，需要你确认提交范围或让我先做一次安全清理分组。\n\n补充已核实：\n- 08:50 全球股市早间要闻今日已成功生成，完成时间 08:55\n- 量化投研主链巡检正常\n- 盘前强检今日已跑过，因此本轮跳过重复执行"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773640284271}}
{"type":"message","id":"410dbe9b","parentId":"ef8b8b88","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:20:27.436Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Monday, March 16th, 2026 — 2:20 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-16 06:20 UTC"}],"timestamp":1773642027435}}
{"type":"message","id":"c5f85ffd","parentId":"410dbe9b","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:20:46.288Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_C2MbZ1s8E9fx0Xe70TaZUANy","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_XdLPkcPZ9fPl3TxMt34ikd1j","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1nO91yBujCDXR2FvUJxVky3f","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773642027436}}
{"type":"message","id":"4409b722","parentId":"c5f85ffd","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:20:46.344Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_C2MbZ1s8E9fx0Xe70TaZUANy","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773642046343}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d7ffdc4","parentId":"4409b722","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:20:46.346Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_XdLPkcPZ9fPl3TxMt34ikd1j","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Quant Ops\n\n## 08:50 Morning News Push Check\n\n### State File\n```bash\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查 `status` / `generated_at` / `last_success_at` / `last_failure_at`\n- [ ] 若交易日 08:50 之后仍无当日成功记录，主动汇报阻断原因\n- [ ] 若 `status` 为 `GENERATION_FAILED` 或 `PUSH_FAILED`，主动汇报错误摘要与日志路径\n- [ ] 若已成功且无新增变化，保持安静\n\n## Quant Research Mainline Health\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.json`\n- 终端摘要：`🩺 量化投研主链巡检：OK/WARN/ALERT`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查退出码与 `overall_status`\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报晨报 / 稳定策略 / 回测队列是哪一项断裂\n- [ ] `WARN`：汇报缺口文件或未生成入口\n- [ ] `OK` 且无新增变化：保持安静\n\n## Trading-day Premarket Precheck (09:20-09:40)\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py --available-cash 1000000 --account-nav 930000\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 无需用户提醒，交易日自动执行\n- [ ] 当日已执行过则跳过\n- [ ] 非交易日保持安静\n- [ ] 失败时主动汇报阻断原因与报告路径\n- [ ] 成功时汇报 `precheck` / `orders` / `brief` 路径\n\n## Daily Strategy Audit\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_strategy_audit.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] `PASS`：简要汇报核心指标与路径\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报未通过项与修复建议\n\n## Daily Enhancements\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_enhancements.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_summary.json`\n- `research/reports/daily_enhancement_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 双源验证失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 热力图失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 正常运行：简要汇报上涨/下跌板块数\n\n## Live Dashboard + Feishu Push\n\n### Commands\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_app_data.py\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_exports.py\npython3 scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_YYYYMMDD.html`\n\n### Push Rules\n- [ ] 成功后主动发飞书 DM：面板路径、precheck 状态、年化/回撤/夏普、买卖记录数、A股温度摘要\n- [ ] `needs_permission=true`：提示给 OpenClaw/终端 Full Disk Access\n- [ ] 导出为空：提示“同花顺暂无可用导出数据/账户为空”\n- [ ] 生成失败：主动发报错摘要与修复建议\n- [ ] 非交易时段不含“可执行买价”，只给预算/优先级/开盘触发条件\n- [ ] 当天已推送且无新增数据，可保持安静\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773642046345}}
{"type":"message","id":"625b77d6","parentId":"5d7ffdc4","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:20:46.348Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1nO91yBujCDXR2FvUJxVky3f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Self-Improvement\n\n## Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/generate_daily_report.py\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_promote_learnings.py --apply --threshold 2\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_extract_skill_drafts.py --threshold 2\n```\n\n## Output\n- `memory/self_improvement_daily_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_autopromote_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_YYYYMMDD.md`\n\n## Rules\n- [ ] 汇总 `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` / `ERRORS.md` / `FEATURE_REQUESTS.md`\n- [ ] 统计高优先级待处理项、状态分布、area 分布\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 自动提升到 `AGENTS.md / TOOLS.md / SOUL.md`\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 生成 skill 草稿到 `skills/<name>/SKILL.md`\n- [ ] **只生成草稿，不自动安装**到 `~/.openclaw/skills/`\n- [ ] 无论有无提升项，都主动发飞书 DM 汇报摘要与三个输出文件路径\n- [ ] 若无提升项，明确写“今日无自动提升项”\n- [ ] 若无技能草稿，明确写“今日无技能草稿生成”\n- [ ] 若发生自动提升，汇报被提升条目、目标文件路径、写入是否成功\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773642046346}}
