{"type":"message","id":"6386ab2d","parentId":"70ddd015","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:21:00.868Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Sf23gjJ2T36n7qI6QFQNaman","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 每日策略审计（20260316）\n\n- 总体状态：`ALERT`（仅反映运行链路）\n- 运行状态：`ALERT`\n- 策略健康度：`PASS`\n- 目标达成：`True`（仅用于策略健康度，年化>=40、回撤<=25、robust_pass=true）\n\n## 运行状态\n- 最近一次自动盘前检查状态：`ok`\n- 盘前自动执行规则：`False`\n- 强制检查门（strict precheck）：`True`\n- 模拟盘对比面板24h内更新（观察项）：`False`\n\n## 策略健康度\n- 回测指标：年化 `55.07%`，回撤 `24.89%`，夏普 `2.794`\n- robust_pass：`True`\n\n## 证据文件\n- summary：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/qlib_breadth_long_turnover_hardcap_relaxed_tuned_summary_20260307_1340.json`\n- auto precheck：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/auto_premarket_precheck_20260316.json`\n- paper comparison dashboard：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_profiles_comparison_latest.html`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773642060867}}
{"type":"message","id":"e892c6b3","parentId":"6386ab2d","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:21:00.870Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5qAX5bxyS07T1Jn0BcoSoszW","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Self-Improvement Daily Report - 2026-03-16\n\n- 生成时间: 2026-03-16 14:20:52\n- 学习条目: 31\n- 错误条目: 4\n- 需求条目: 1\n- 待关注高优先级: 17\n- 可自动提升条目: 0\n\n## 状态分布\n- pending: 32\n- promoted: 2\n- resolved: 2\n\n## 优先级分布\n- critical: 1\n- high: 18\n- low: 4\n- medium: 13\n\n## Area 分布\n- backend: 5\n- config: 8\n- docs: 18\n- infra: 3\n- tests: 2\n\n## 高优先级待处理\n- LRN-20260308-002 | high | pending | 用户指出“多账户持仓抓取不准”，核心问题是把“账本缓存可读”误当作“账户切换已生效”，导致连续三轮结果一致却未在第一时间明确说明采集口径受限。\n- LRN-20260315-006 | high | pending | For future XTP integration, isolate all XTP SDK calls in a subprocess; never call InsertOrder directly from the main Python process due to callback deadlock risk\n- LRN-20260315-007 | high | pending | Do not mix XTP trading market enums with quote exchange enums; they are reversed between Shanghai and Shenzhen\n- LRN-20260315-008 | high | pending | Outside trading hours, XTP paper trading may reject limit orders because quotes are unavailable; scheduling must gate order placement to market hours\n- LRN-20260315-009 | high | pending | AKShare full-market A-share endpoint stock_zh_a_spot_em may fail outside mainland China; use single-stock queries or alternate data source fallback\n- LRN-20260315-010 | high | pending | Do not let AI generate stock picks or reports without an explicit data-backed decision path; ban vague 'common sense' justification\n- LRN-20260315-011 | high | pending | Preferred quant research system architecture: OpenClaw orchestration + multi-search MCP layer + layered market data + XTP subprocess isolation + cron-based monitoring windows\n- LRN-20260315-012 | high | pending | Do not restate external quant architecture as-is; adapt the system description to Zhang Ling's actual data stack, which includes Tushare and Yahoo Finance\n- LRN-20260315-013 | high | pending | When corrected on prior statements, revisit the workspace evidence before summarizing architecture; do not overwrite yesterday's documented data-source policy with a generic external template\n- LRN-20260315-014 | high | pending | When asked to learn from external examples, extract strengths and adapt them to the existing system instead of copying the architecture wholesale\n- LRN-20260315-015 | high | pending | Do not ask Zhang Ling whether to continue for procedural optimization work; continue automatically and interrupt only for important decisions\n- LRN-20260316-001 | high | pending | Asynchronous promises to continue work later must be converted into a verifiable execution chain in the same turn\n- LRN-20260316-002 | high | pending | Do not claim 'I’ll continue pushing app optimization myself' without verifiable follow-through in the stated time window\n- LRN-20260316-004 | high | pending | Do not promise '中午前修复' without device-level validation; report missed deadline directly\n- LRN-20260316-005 | high | pending | After user says 'programmatic tasks don't ask me', proactively report new artifacts without waiting to be asked\n- LRN-20260316-007 | high | pending | 在“来福投研会”群聊中必须以投研组织语境发言，不能把主会话的英语学习产品职责直接套用到该群\n- ERR-20260308-001 | critical | pending | 向用户直接回传了内部错误字符串：`403 OpenAI codex passthrough requires a non-empty instructions field`，影响沟通体验。 ClawHub registry unreachable when attempting to inspect/install camoufox-cli Heartbeat dashboard generation failed because scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py is missing in personal-a-share-research-system memory_store failed because LanceDB native module is missing on this host Daily investment research org runner failed once due to unterminated string literal in orchestrator markdown renderer Manual morning-news test could not use web_search because Brave API key is missing Role briefing generator failed once due to unterminated string literal in markdown section headers web_search unavailable because Brave API key is not configured on this host Shell probe for Android emulator tooling failed due to unmatched quote in printf block run_investment_research_review_ledger.py used JSON null literal in Python dict and crashed on first run Review ledger script selected the wrong org report because it sorted wildcard matches lexicographically instead of by freshness Overnight automation had a visible idle gap from 00:20 to 07:00 and the 08:50 morning report landed late at 08:54-08:55 Night autopilot instruction was treated as a plan document instead of a real scheduled execution chain, causing a 00:20-07:00 idle gap and missed 07:30 report Browser snapshot timed out after opening search result tabs, blocking browser-based web research fallback Progress on research-organization build was too slow because work stayed reactive and patch-driven instead of queue-driven and acceptance-oriented\n\n## 可自动提升候选\n- 无\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773642060869}}
