{"type":"message","id":"4484aaa9","parentId":"2b438153","timestamp":"2026-03-16T11:29:23.680Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The generate_live_global_dashboard.py doesn't exist anywhere in the workspace. This is a failure - the script is missing. According to the heartbeat rules:- \"实盘面板生成失败或需要权限：主动发报错摘要与修复建议\"\n\nI need to report this. The ths_app_data.py worked (found holdings/trades), but the export sync and dashboard generation failed.\n\nLet me report the findings:1. Daily enhancements: dual source WARN (1/4 valid), heatmap OK (436 up / 61 down)2. Live dashboard: FAILED - generate_live_global_dashboard.py is missing\n\nThis is an active alert situation.","thinkingSignature":"d9ceddab72fc2f8eb0d62105eb11b246ddb2c640795ee2769db5713ff326c183"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 有新结果，需要提醒：\n\n**1. 每日量化增强 - 已完成**\n- 双源验证：WARN（4支股票中1支有效，腾讯vs新浪价格差异较大）\n- 板块热力图：OK（上涨436个板块 / 下跌61个板块）\n- 文件：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_enhancement_20260316.json`\n\n**2. 实盘面板生成 - 失败**\n- `sync_ths_exports.py`：未找到对应脚本\n- `generate_live_global_dashboard.py`：脚本不存在\n- ths_app_data.py 同步成功：获取到44条持仓、261条交易记录\n- 阻断原因：项目目录中缺少 `generate_live_global_dashboard.py` 脚本\n- 修复建议：确认该脚本是否已迁移或重命名，或从其他位置复制到当前项目\n\n**3. 今日已核实项目**\n- 08:50 晨报：已成功\n- 量化投研主链巡检：OK\n- 盘前强检：已执行\n- 每日策略审计：ALERT（之前已报）"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":38436,"output":396,"cacheRead":22695,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61527,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773660556017}}
